CME Saves

  Monica, shown as imperial
  Kye, shown as Nord
  Brianna, shown as imperial

  Mods Required

  Enhanced Character Edit by ECE team

  The Eyes Of Beauty by Gabriel Mailhot
  Calientes Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE- by Caliente
  SG Female Textures Renewal by Hello Santa
  ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii
  SG Female Eyebrows by Hello Santa
  Better Females Eyebrows - Standalone by [b]BellaGail and Kalilies
[/b]  SG Hair by Hello Santa
  Show Race Menu Precache Killer by [b]Kapaer[/b]
  [url=http://www.google.co.uk/url?sa=t&rct=j&q=&esrc=s&source=web&cd=1&cad=rja&uact=8&ved=0CCMQFjAA&url=http%3A%2F%2Fskse.silverlock.org%2F&ei=-KdRVIHhKcvlav27gegF&usg=AFQjCNFwocpBnh12wr8ASqVU_3APr056Hw&bvm=bv.78597519,d.d2s]Skyrim Script Extender (SKSE)[/url]

  To install copy and paste the Tri File, in to the CME_save Folder
  Located at Documents/My Games/Skyrim
 
  Optional
  Also included is a fitness body for CBBE  i made for a few  characters
  To install this copy and paste the femalebody_1_msn.dds, file
  Into the female folder
  Located at Skyrim>Data>Textures>Actors>Characters>Female
